task.summary: Minor IDE changes, gradle config update.
UI Overhaul - changed ic_launcher, revamped color specs. Also removed EditActivity, editing now handled in ViewActivity.

Updates
1. Migrating content view to fragments. 2. Removed "emptyview". 3. Tasks updated from 2nd Task screen, no more 'task edit view'. 4. New login and sign up screens.
